data.description: New Price Adjustment! Great starter or retirement home in the very desirable Chimney Lakes subdivision. Already priced at a discount so you can add your personal touches. Create your forever home or acquire as a great rental investment opportunity. This 3 Bedroom, 2 full bath split plan home features a huge central family room, wood-burning fireplace, formal dining area and kitchen with separate eating space. A new architectural shingle roof just installed 11/2023 and new water heater 8/2023. HVAC previously replaced in 2013. Large enclosed Florida room, easy to maintain vinyl siding. Chimney Lakes Gazebo Park is nearby plus there is an array of other local recreational facilities including other playgrounds, pool, tennis and other amenities. Home sold as-is. Seller will not consider or counter low-ball, sight unseen investor offers. This is not a distressed sale!
